Jefferson building completed in 1897.

00:02:02.460 --> 00:02:06.890 position:66%
There are two other buildings on Capitol
Hill in addition to the Jefferson building

00:02:06.890 --> 00:02:11.110 position:66%
that comprise the library on Capitol Hill.

00:02:11.110 --> 00:02:13.520
We also have some off-site storage.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:17.990
