00:08:26.820 --> 00:08:31.780 position:64%
You can see there's a red circle around
select the format of your primary source,

00:08:31.780 --> 00:08:34.820 position:72%
and then another red circle around a question.

00:08:34.820 --> 00:08:37.830
Clicking on that question
will bring up a question.

00:08:37.830 --> 00:08:41.130
Clicking on that question
icon will bring up a question.

00:08:41.130 --> 00:08:47.640 position:67%
